#: ../../source/cloud/oci.rst:2
msgid "容器标准"
msgstr "Container Standards"

#: ../../source/cloud/oci.rst:5
msgid "OCI"
msgstr "OCI"

#: ../../source/cloud/oci.rst:6
msgid "开放容器标准 (Open Container Initiative, OCI) 是用于规范容器格式和运行时行业标准。目前OCI提出的规范有："
msgstr ""
"The Open Container Initiative (OCI) is an industry standard for specifying "
"container formats and runtimes. The specifications currently proposed by OCI "
"include:"

#: ../../source/cloud/oci.rst:8
msgid ""
"`OCI Runtime Specification <https://github.com/opencontainers/runtime-"
"spec>`_"
msgstr ""
"`OCI Runtime Specification <https://github.com/opencontainers/runtime-"
"spec>`_"

#: ../../source/cloud/oci.rst:9
msgid "`OCI Image Format <https://github.com/opencontainers/image-spec>`_"
msgstr "`OCI Image Format <https://github.com/opencontainers/image-spec>`_"

#: ../../source/cloud/oci.rst:10
msgid ""
"`OCI Distribution Specification <https://github.com/opencontainers"
"/distribution-spec>`_"
msgstr ""
"`OCI Distribution Specification <https://github.com/opencontainers"
"/distribution-spec>`_"

#: ../../source/cloud/oci.rst:13
msgid "CRI"
msgstr "CRI"

#: ../../source/cloud/oci.rst:14
msgid ""
"容器运行时 (Container Runtime Interface, CRI) "
"定义了容器和镜像的接口，目前官方支持的容器运行时包括Docker、Containerd、CRI-O和frakti。"
msgstr ""
"The Container Runtime Interface (CRI) defines the interfaces for containers "
"and images. The officially supported container runtimes currently include "
"Docker, Containerd, CRI-O, and frakti."

#: ../../source/cloud/oci.rst:17
msgid "参考链接"
msgstr "References"

#: ../../source/cloud/oci.rst:20
msgid "文档"
msgstr "Documentation"

#: ../../source/cloud/oci.rst:21
msgid ""
"`Introducing Container Runtime Interface (CRI) in Kubernetes "
"<https://kubernetes.io/blog/2016/12/container-runtime-interface-cri-in-"
"kubernetes/>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Introducing Container Runtime Interface (CRI) in Kubernetes "
"<https://kubernetes.io/blog/2016/12/container-runtime-interface-cri-in-"
"kubernetes/>`_"

#: ../../source/cloud/oci.rst:22
msgid "`cri-o <https://cri-o.io/>`_"
msgstr "`cri-o <https://cri-o.io/>`_"

#: ../../source/cloud/oci.rst:25
msgid "实现"
msgstr "Implementations"

#: ../../source/cloud/oci.rst:26
msgid "`runc <https://github.com/opencontainers/runc>`_ OCI Runtime 的参考实现"
msgstr ""
"`runc <https://github.com/opencontainers/runc>`_ reference implementation of"
" the OCI Runtime"

#: ../../source/cloud/oci.rst:27
msgid ""
"`Kata Containers <https://github.com/kata-containers/kata-containers>`_ "
"提供高性能的硬件虚拟化容器运行时"
msgstr ""
"`Kata Containers <https://github.com/kata-containers/kata-containers>`_ "
"provides a high-performance hardware-virtualized container runtime"

#: ../../source/cloud/oci.rst:28
msgid "`gvisor <https://github.com/google/gvisor>`_ Go 实现的基于用户态内核的容器运行时"
msgstr ""
"`gvisor <https://github.com/google/gvisor>`_ a Go implementation of a "
"container runtime based on a user-space kernel"

#: ../../source/cloud/oci.rst:29
msgid "`buildkit <https://github.com/moby/buildkit>`_ docker build 拆分出来的build项目"
msgstr ""
"`buildkit <https://github.com/moby/buildkit>`_ a build project split out "
"from docker build"
